	<h1 class="title">“同夫”婚姻在中国：娶了女同的直男们</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/112251/small/112251.png?1431932514" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">纽约时报 Didi Kirsten Tatlow</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-05-18 12:00:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/9616/medium/9616.jpg?1436675388" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


